data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Motivated seller. Move-In Ready Home in Promenade Estates at Palmer Ranch! Why opt for the delays of new construction when this pristine residence in the sought-after Promenade Estates of Palmer Ranch awaits? Located west of I-75 off Honore Avenue, this gem offers the benefits of a gated, amenity-rich community. Highlights include a sunlit open floor plan with rich ceramic tiles and a bright transom window. The gourmet kitchen has ample storage, granite countertops, stainless appliances, and an inviting breakfast bar. Seamless transition from indoor to outdoor with sliding doors opening to the largest lot in the community. Fences are allowed if you wish. Main bedroom retreat has an expansive en suite, featuring a walk-in shower, dual sinks, and generous closet space. Three additional bedrooms, offering flexibility for home office, den, or studio. Convenient indoor laundry with appliances included. Spacious two-car garage, perfect for vehicles or even a golf cart. Newer construction also saves on your insurance bill, currently only $1250 annually. Community Amenities: Lush pool with designated swim lanes.  Fun playground and splash zone. . Recreation areas including sand volleyball and basketball courts. State-of-the-art fitness center. Pet-friendly with dedicated dog parks and grooming stations. This home offers unparalleled proximity to A-rated schools, pristine beaches, exquisite dining, shopping, and the celebrated arts and culture of Sarasota and Venice. Don't let this opportunity slip away – book your private tour now!
